Week 16:
Draft your self-assessment
Submit to shared Google Drive folder
Schedule your collaborative conversation using provided link
Finals Week: Collaborative conversations (15-20 minutes each)
Final grades posted: Within one week of your conversation

Questions About Grading?
If you have questions about the self-assessment approach, what constitutes strong evidence, or how to make your case effectively, please ask early in the semester. Office hours are available for grading discussions throughout the course.
