Send course emails to [your email] with subject line: "TGE-Ethics-[Section]: [Topic]"
I respond within 24 hours on business days (Monday-Friday, 8am-5pm). Use professional format: greeting, clear message, your name.
How Feedback Works
Your Google Drive folder contains all your work—drafts, AI transcripts, revisions. I can see it in real-time, so I monitor your progress weekly rather than grading batches of assignments.
AI gives you immediate feedback on grammar, organization, clarity, and revision suggestions throughout your writing process.
I provide human judgment on things AI can't assess: Is your project authentic? Are you actually learning? Can you assess your own work? Are you stuck?
When You'll Hear From Me
I'll reach out if:
You haven't progressed in 2+ weeks
Your work shows confusion or concerns
You've missed a required checkpoint
