Syllabus and Course Changes
This syllabus is adaptable. To the degree possible, this syllabus represents the totality of course assignments, policies, and course procedures. However, I reserve the right to change relevant features of the course in order to maximize pedagogical utility. I will seek input from the class whenever appropriate, and changes will be updated on Canvas.

